These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Job: coach, teacher, project-manager, nurse
1. Job:nurse is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Job:teacher##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Job:project-manager is on the left or right of Job:nurse##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Job        | coach | teacher   | nurse | project-manager    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Transport: train, roller, skateboard, boat
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Transport:roller is on the left of Transport:boat##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Transport:train##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Transport:train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Transport   | skateboard | train  | roller  | boat |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Pet: rabbit, ferret, turtle, cat
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Pet:cat is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Pet:turtle is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Pet:ferret##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Pet:ferret is on the right of Pet:turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Pet          | cat | turtle | ferret    | rabbit      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
