1. Job:doctor is between Music-Genre:blues and Music-Genre:reggae##2
2. Job:entrepreneur is on the left of Job:project-manager##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Job:project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

