2. House:futuristic is on the left of House:farmhouse##1
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
4. House:ranch-style == Movie-Genre:epic##1
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of House:farmhouse##3
6. House:palace is on the right of House:farmhouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| House     | ranch-style | futuristic  | farmhouse     | palace |

