Pet: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left or right of Hobby:singing##3
2. Hobby:hiking is in an odd position##4
3. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left or right of Hobby:hiking##3
4. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. Hobby:collecting is between Hobby:hiking and Hobby:singing##2
6. Pet:fish is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:fish is between Hobby:collecting and Pet:goat##2
8. Hobby:collecting is on the left or right of Hobby:singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | singing | collecting      | hiking | card-games |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

