.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
Color: light-blue, pink, red, apricot
1. Beverage:almond-milk == Color:apricot##1
2. Color:light-blue is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Color:apricot is between Color:light-blue and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Color:apricot is on the left or right of Color:light-blue##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Color:pink##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Color   | red | pink | apricot        | light-blue    |

