2. Sport:ice-hockey == Cigar:pall-mall##1
3. Sport:cricket == Cigar:old-henry##1
4. Cigar:game is on the left or right of Cigar:old-henry##3
5. Cigar:pall-mall is in an even position##4
6. Cigar:game is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | pall-mall | game    | old-henry |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

