.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Sport: lacrosse, badminton, golf, snowboarding
Food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. Food:kale is on the far left##1
2. Sport:golf is on the left or right of Sport:lacrosse##3
3. Sport:snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of Sport:lacrosse##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == Sport:badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | lacrosse    | golf       | badminton |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

