3. Music-Genre:rock is between Job:entrepreneur and Music-Genre:classical##2
4. Job:manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. Music-Genre:electronic is on the right of Job:software-developer##1
6. Music-Genre:electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Music-Genre   | ambient          | rock | classical         | electronic  |

 